ğŸ“„ README.md
# Save the Watermelon

A terminal-based word guessing game where you must save the watermelon by guessing the secret word before the slice counter runs out.

## How to Run
```bash
python -m src.game
# or
python src/game.py

How to Test

Run the tests manually or with Pythonâ€™s built-in unittest:

python -m unittest discover tests

Features & Rules

Random secret word from the list.

Guess one letter per turn.

Each incorrect guess removes a slice.

Win if you reveal all letters before slices run out.

Lose if slices reach 0.

Input validation for single alphabetic characters.

Displays progress after every guess.

Option to replay.

Known Issues / Limitations

No word categories or difficulty levels.

No ASCII art stages.

Only English words included.

Credits

Developed for the â€œSave the Watermelonâ€ Python project assignment.


